<br>
&quot;A tale you say, well I can certainly weave a tale to entertain.&quot; Casidy smiled warmly at the challenge. It was a challenge wasn't it, she had thought that was the intent behind the message. Bah, how could anyone ever hope to compete at tale weaving save for another bard, this was after all her profession. <br>
<br>
